text: Georg Utz (born 22 August 1935) is a German wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle middleweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1935 births Category:Living people Category:People from Kornwestheim Category:People from the Free People's State of Württemberg Category:German male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of the United Team of Germany Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics
